---
title: Cheesy-Topped Chicken with Fries & Creamy Slaw
description: Pair juicy chicken thighs with our homely Aussie spice blend and you’ve got a match made in heaven. With a
topping of gooey Cheddar cheese and oven-baked fries wanting to join in on the fun, we just couldn’t say no.
More is more in our books, and you’ll love us for it!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
